---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Ship Week — Data Divas">
  <main class="container-narrow" style="padding-top: var(--space-2xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Ship Week</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        <strong>One lab. One week. One demo day.</strong>
      </p>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
        A weekly cadence where the community picks a lab, ships it, and demos what they built.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="https://discord.gg/XXUk8y5MTT" class="btn btn-primary">join_ship_week()</a>
        <a href="/labs" class="btn btn-outline">browse_labs()</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="code-divider" />

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section>
      <h2>// How It Works</h2>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-badge">
            <span class="badge badge-green">Monday</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">Lab Announced</div>
            <p>Community votes or maintainer picks the lab for the week. Get your environment ready and read the requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-badge">
            <span class="badge badge-cyan">Tue-Fri</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">Ship Mode</div>
            <p>Build, break things, fix them, and document everything. Share progress in Discord. Help others when stuck.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-badge">
            <span class="badge badge-pink">Sunday</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">Demo Day</div>
            <p>2-minute demos in Discord voice. Show what you built, what broke, and how you fixed it. No slides needed—just your terminal and repo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="code-divider" />

    <!-- Demo Format -->
    <section>
      <h2>// Demo Format (2 minutes)</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
        Keep it real. Keep it short. We want to see what you shipped.
      </p>

      <div class="demo-checklist">
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <code class="terminal-prompt">$</code>
          <div>
            <strong>What I built</strong>
            <p>Quick walkthrough of your implementation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <code class="terminal-prompt">$</code>
          <div>
            <strong>Biggest tradeoff</strong>
            <p>The decision that mattered most</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <code class="terminal-prompt">$</code>
          <div>
            <strong>What broke</strong>
            <p>The gnarliest bug or blocker you hit</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <code class="terminal-prompt">$</code>
          <div>
            <strong>How I fixed it</strong>
            <p>Your solution or workaround</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <code class="terminal-prompt">$</code>
          <div>
            <strong>What I'd do next</strong>
            <p>If you had more time, what would you improve?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="code-divider" />

    <!-- Ship Requirements -->
    <section>
      <h2>// Ship Requirements</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">
        To get credit for shipping, you need these artifacts:
      </p>

      <div class="requirements-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="tech-badge">required</div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Repo Link</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem;">
            Public GitHub repo with your code
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="tech-badge">required</div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Demo or Screenshots</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem;">
            Proof that it actually works
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="tech-badge">required</div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Write-up</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem;">
            README with tradeoffs, what broke, and the fix
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="tech-badge">required</div>
          <h3 style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">2 Resume Bullets</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem;">
            How you'd describe this on your resume
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="code-divider" />

    <!-- Why Ship Week -->
    <section>
      <h2>// Why Ship Week?</h2>

      <div class="benefits-list">
        <div class="benefit-item">
          <span class="badge badge-green">accountability</span>
          <p>Weekly deadline keeps you shipping, not just learning</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">community</span>
          <p>Learn from others' solutions and debugging approaches</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
          <span class="badge badge-pink">portfolio</span>
          <p>Build 52 real projects a year with receipts</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit-item">
          <span class="badge badge-orange">skills</span>
          <p>Practice explaining technical decisions under time pressure</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="terminal-cta">
      <div class="terminal" style="margin-top: var(--space-2xl); font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: center;">
        <span style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Ready to ship?</span><br/>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/XXUk8y5MTT" style="color: var(--cyan); font-weight: 600;">discord.join()</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .timeline-badge {
    min-width: 100px;
    padding-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .timeline-item .card {
    flex: 1;
  }

  /* Demo Checklist */
  .demo-checklist {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .checklist-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .terminal-prompt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    min-width: 30px;
  }

  .checklist-item strong {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--purple-300);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .checklist-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Requirements Grid */
  .requirements-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  /* Benefits List */
  .benefits-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .benefit-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  /* Terminal CTA */
  .terminal-cta .terminal {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .terminal-cta .terminal::before {
    content: '';
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .timeline-badge {
      min-width: auto;
    }

    .requirements-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
